<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                durch<expan>lewchtigst<ex>en</ex></expan> fürsten und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund,</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>em</ex></expan> und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.
                        künigs, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, also tun wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> ze wissen, daz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch künig, allhie zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> lantfrid gemacht und berett hat
                                <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> den <expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <add>als</add> die hie gewest sein, und
                        uns und <expan>etlich<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>stett<ex>en,</ex></expan> die denn vormals
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> lantfrid
                            <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> gehabt
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, die <expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>lantfr<ex>id</ex></expan>
<expan>jecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> hie gesworn. Und also ist
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, der <expan>r<ex>ömisch</ex></expan> künig, auf
                                <expan>gest<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von uns
                            <expan>aufgebroch<ex>en</ex></expan> und gen Kadelspurg
                                <expan>geritte<ex>n</ex></expan>; und ist uns gesagt, daz er gen
                        Winsheim und gen <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ziehen well.<pb facs="#facs_80" id="40r"/> Wa er <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> fürbas das hawbt
                        hin keren und ziehen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, wissen wir niht
                                <expan>aigensch<ex>aft</ex></expan>; also
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
                        mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, ob ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan> frawen, der künigin, zukunft iht
                        aigenschaft <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> hett
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemt</expan> und ob
                        ir icht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewff west
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> erfürt, die uns ze
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>, daz ir uns das bey
                            <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> zu stund bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> kost
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet,
                                <expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch auch
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> ob
                        wir icht erfüren. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>fra<ex>n</ex>cisci.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> den von Ulme
                            <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan> und <expan>ausgenom<ex>en</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frawen, der <expan>künigin,</expan>
                        niht <expan>zu schreibe<ex>n.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
